    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We tested an operationally efficient way to pool samples on a rapid, point-of-care PCR device and examined the limit of detection of SARS-CoV-2 for various pool sizes. Pooled testing maintained testing performance similar to individual sample PCR testing, offering the potential for scalable rapid testing at lower cost with less supplies.</jats:p>",
